data.title: MEETINGS - Conference entitled Law, government & the health service (UK) March 2001:
data.meta_description: Emap public sector management events and the Health Service Journal will hold Law, government & the health service, a conference for health managers, at the Shaw Park Plaza Hotel, London, UK, on March 22-23. For more information contact Emap in the UK. Tel: +44 (0) 7874 0294. Fax: +44 (0) 7874 0298. Email: healthcare.conference@emap.com
